Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.44,0:32:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about I feel like I have\Na difficult time um allowing myself and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.36,0:32:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,accepting myself to be loved and I feel\Nlike that's a hindrance to knowing get
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.79,0:32:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,moving on to knowing the love of God.\N>> All right. So when people are loving
