Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.96,0:32:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,>> There's nothing to accept or reject.\NAnd it also represents of course uh
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.67,0:32:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,their capacity for lovingness. You see?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.60,0:33:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So if they're unloving towards you, it\Ndoesn't mean that you are unlovable
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.39,0:33:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it takes a while to sort out.\NUh your your willingness to give love is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.48,0:33:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what uh determines your capacity to\Nreceive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.48,0:33:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't worry about being loved.\NJust be loving towards all of life and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.88,0:33:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all of its expressions.\NEvery little toad, every tree,
