Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.24,0:33:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,dignity and wonder.\NAnd that will bring me to know the love
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.27,0:33:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of God.\N>> God is all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.15,0:33:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\NSo when you appreciate the beauty of a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.39,0:33:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,tree, the beauty of a flower,\Nthe magnificent of a bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.51,0:34:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then you see you witness God.\NThere's the famous story of the hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.08,0:34:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,who shoot goes duck hunting and he\Nshoots down this duck. The duck comes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.84,0:34:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,flying down like this, lands on the\Nground, and then its mate comes down and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.11,0:34:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,lays over the duck and covers its mate\Nwith its wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.76,0:34:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,50,000 hunters quit hunting after they\Nwitnessed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.63,0:34:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing was said,\Nbut you get the essence of that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.20,0:34:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,50,000 hunters gave up hunting.\NMy father was they tried to teach him
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.67,0:34:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,how to hunt\Nand he had a a dough right in his sights
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.32,0:34:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and he looked through the the site and\Nhe saw this the magnificence of this
