Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.44,0:35:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go to any store and buy venison\Nfor God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.68,0:35:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the significance and the meaning\Ndepends on the context, the cultural
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.83,0:35:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,context, the time and the setting. You\Nknow,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.48,0:35:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 20s, uh, bringing home a deer was\Na worthwhile endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.16,0:35:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, you can just go to Walmart and\Nthey got it right in the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.96,0:36:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yep. Better to pray to Walmart.\NYou know, I love Walmart.
