Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> No.\N>> Okay. If I miss something, you call it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.00,0:36:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to my attention\Nbecause I got to deal with the lights
