Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.00,0:37:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so the mind says well if it is then it\Nexists.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.92,0:37:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind that said that the mind\Nsaid that what does the mind know about
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.24,0:37:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it? It doesn't know anything about it.\NIt wouldn't even try to answer the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.59,0:37:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,question if it understood it.\NIf the existence had no reality, there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.52,0:38:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,would be nothing to ask the question.\NSo it answers itself by contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.07,0:38:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I faced that conundrum. I remember at\Nage three.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.32,0:38:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was suddenly stunningly hit by the\Nfact that I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.64,0:38:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute I realized that I exist, a\Ntremendous fear came up. If I exist, it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.28,0:38:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,might have come about uh that I would\Nnot have existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.40,0:38:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So then I thought which is reality\Nexistence or non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.35,0:38:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All this was done with knowingness and\Nnot a mental verbalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.56,0:38:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am came as a terrible shock\Nbecause I came out of non-existence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.72,0:38:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,nonawareness of existence into awareness\Nof existence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.92,0:39:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was like suddenly the cleague\Nlights were turned on it was blinding
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.64,0:39:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and shattering. Mhm.\NSo those are just moments in the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.88,0:39:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution of a certain consciousness as\N>> Thank you. And I have these two crosses
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.83,0:39:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that I bought. Um I wondered if you\Nwould bless them for my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I have permission to bless these\Ncrosses. Just I bless these crosses in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.07,0:39:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,thy name, O Lord.\NYes.
