Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.44,1:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,fear about many things. How can I\Ntranslate transcend these tendencies?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.08,1:09:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Fear. He wants to let go of fear.\NYou can only do it by trusting God and
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.12,1:09:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,asking God for guidance. And then you\Nhave to take a leap of faith. You have
