Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.08,1:10:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Very special. I don't know why,\Nbut they are. Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.52,1:11:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm.\NYes,
